gl%3DUS" class="rapid-with-clickid"><ins>专用的 Assistant 应用程序</ins></a>，例如<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-assistant-samsung-galaxy-watch-4-153001003.html"><ins>Samsung Galaxy Watch 4</ins></a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/fossil-finally-gets-google-assistant-on-its-wear-os-3-smartwatches-194519611.html"><ins>Fossil 智能手表</ins></a>，当然<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-watch-review-battery-life-fitbit-heart-rate-sensing-015412121.html"><ins>还有 Pixel Watch</ins></a> 。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>此举将影响许多 2020 年及之前的旧手表，包括 Tag Heuer、Mobvoi、Motorola、Oppo、小米、Misfit、Casio 和 LG 的型号。维基百科有一个<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Wear_OS_devices"><ins>有用的 Wear OS 设备列表</ins></a>以及它们支持的最新版本的操作系统。然而，由于它是维基百科，因此值得在其他地方仔细检查，以确认您的手表实际上是否可以运行 Wear OS 3。</p><p>目前尚不清楚谷歌计划何时终止这些旧手表上的助理支持。不过，如果您在 Wear OS 2 设备上依赖 Assistant，您可能希望尽快升级。碰巧的是，谷歌预计将在未来几个月内<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-will-reportedly-release-pixel-watch-2-this-fall-213015367.html"><ins>推出第二款 Pixel Watch</ins></a> 。该公司通常每年十月举办一次大型硬件活动。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/older-wear-os-devices-will-soon-lose-google-assistant-support-180004200.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/older-wear-os-devices-will-soon-lose-google-assistant-support-180004200.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d24ab606-eb58-4e4a-9adf-3d088fca5700</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 16 Aug 2023 18:00:04 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692208452</ingested><modified> 2023-08-16T17:54:22+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|